<h3 id="tables">Tables</h3>
<p>
	Tables are in fact not made with real shortcodes but very simple <a href="https://www.w3schools.com/html/html_tables.asp" target="_blank">html tables</a>.
</p>
<p>
	They must be inserted in the <b>Text</b> page editor or in the Text widget. Look at the images bellow:
</p>
<img src="images/table-text.jpg" alt="Table Text" width="1905" height="952">
<img src="images/table-widget.jpg" alt="Table Widget" width="1905" height="952">
<p>
